Hello Avicus Network!
I am thinking of making a 200 Subscribers Montage!
I would like your help to assist me in making this video because my time on the computer and YouTube is limited due to college.
So! The layout is the following!

Title Of The Video
Date Of When It Was Uploaded
Time Stamp of What You Think Should be Selected
YouTube URL

The videos MUST be from my channel and no one else's! Anyone who get accepted and I use there submission will be accredited at the end of the video!
